dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Sawyer County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Sawyer_Roads_2016.gdb.[The address range is a linear feature class that contains the high-low, left-right attributes for addresses. This feature class is used for geo coding and may also be used to support dispatching.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
